import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter, Route, Routes} from "react-router-dom"
import Dashboard from './Dashboard/Dashboard'

  return <>

  <Routes>
<Route path='/' element={<Dashboard/>}/>

  </Routes>
  
  </BrowserRouter>
  
  </>
}

export default App
